title: what happens in chicago stays in chicago
itunes:title: what happens in chicago stays in chicago
description:
Brooke and Danielle are LIVE from CHICAGO!  The gals went to Chicago for Lollapalooza and they are recapping all of the craziness from the weekend.  Join Brooke and Danielle from their hotel room getting ~real~ about what went down at the festival!  Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening stories + screenshots on Instagram.

Brooke’s Instagram https://www.instagram.com/brookemiccio/
